name: Rosettes on Twine
description:
Cute single rosette on a twine headband. This headband is open, so you can tie it on or braid it into your hair-do! Length is 25-30 inches. This will fit children and adults.

***Not recommended for infants***

Shipping note: If you are local to Huntley, IL and want to inquire about pickup options, please contact me BEFORE placing your order to avoid shipping charges.

name: Winter/Christmas/Yule Cards
description:
Fun, colorful, and elegant cards to send out your thoughts, well wishes, and words of encouragement.

These are flat cards - they do not open. The back is blank so that you can add a message. Approx. Size: 4.25in x 5.5in. Each card comes with a white envelope.

Please make a selection based on the order of the photos (1, 2, 3, etc.) to choose the card style you would like.

Please note - pattern location may vary from card to card.

Shipping note: If you are local to Huntley, IL and want to inquire about pickup options, please contact me BEFORE placing your order to avoid shipping charges.
